    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "BUSINESS\nCIASS\nMEN U\nU UNITED",
      "LUNCHEON SERVICE\nCOCKTAIL SERVICE\nA Ramekin of Toasted Mixed Nuts\nserved with Your Favorite Cocktail or Beverage.\nAPPETIZER\nEnjoy a Selection of Gravlax, Crayfish Medallion\nand Terrine of Capon.\nWINE SELECTIONS\nVeuve Clicquot Ponsardin Brut\nMedoc Baron Philippe 1986\nLatour Chardonnay 1987\nSeppelt's Chardonnay\nSALAD\nCrisp Salad Greens lightly tossed.\nHazelnut Vinaigrette Dressing.\nU UnITED\nENTREE SELECTIONS\nFILET MIGNON\nGrilled Center-Cut Tenderloin of Beef enhanced by\na Béarnaise Sauce of Shallots and White Wine.\nAccompanied with Fondante Potatoes and Green Beans.\nSALMON FLORENTINE\nPoached New Zealand Salmon Steak wrapped in Tender\nSpinach Leaves and topped with Champagne Sauce. Presented\nwith Parsley Potatoes, Green Beans and Carrots.\nDESSERT\nMANGO MOUSSE\nSatin-Smooth Mango Mousse served in a\nLuscious Chocolate Shell.\nWe apologize if occasionally your choice is not available."
    ],
